{"tid":1404487,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【85罷工攻略】想唔想令港鐵全線一齊夢遊！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T04:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T22:46:57.000Z","uid":146499,"like":45,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"18924f91ae50a94b7c9460d1c0b6bc684eab096f","tid":1404487,"uid":146499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"代友po<br />\n<br />\n話說我認識一位電子工程師，佢負責港鐵電力系統多年，所以我趁機問問佢港鐵相關嘅電力設施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n畢竟呢啲都係重要嘅常識，作為良好市民，如果見可疑人物鬼鬼祟祟接近嗰個地方，我哋都有責任阻止佢係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢話電力房有密碼鎖，一般好難解破，非常安全，叫我哋唔好擔心。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不過佢話有一個方法好難防，就係帶<span style=\"color: red;\">金屬氣球</span>。</span><br />\n <br />\n大家應該知道港鐵安全守則中，其中一條係唔好帶金屬氣球入閘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁講係有原因嘅，因為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">萬一金屬氣球飄入隧道，觸及頂部電纜，就會導致漏電。為安全起見，港鐵一定會停駛。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>咁如果有大量金屬氣球飄入隧道，又入咗啲好難清嘅位，咁港鐵唔停翻幾個鐘都恢復唔到。</strong></span>重點係如果多線齊發&hellip;&hellip;基本上就玩完了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以佢提醒大家一見人攞金屬氣球入閘就要喝止佢，如果唔係好危險，我哋有責任保障他人安全，係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n工程師仲拜託我哋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">守護港鐵一個重要據點&mdash;&mdash;就係控制中心</span></span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n控制中心有三個，分別喺<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">青衣</span>、<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">九龍灣</span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">火炭</span>。<br />\n青衣嘅主要控制以前嘅地鐵線（紅藍綠三線、東涌線、迪士尼線、將軍澳線）同西鐵。火炭係東鐵同馬鐵，九龍灣係後備用，主要用嚟觀察鐵路狀況。平日港鐵係用自動系統，但可以用手動指令凌駕，而控制中心就可做到呢一點。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">控制中心可以令所有鐵路停駛，但事關中心同安全系統都有關，如果搞到佢，又控制唔好都幾大鑊</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以如生事之徒未必識點操縱系統，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">佢哋可能會選擇圍堵控制中心，令佢停止運作。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果我哋見到有人想包圍果棟建築，一定要叫埋啲街坊落嚟睇睇咩情況，一有異常就一齊幫手阻止。我諗大家點都會唔想港九新界鐵路全面停駛㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n暫時係咁多，大家搭車一定要注意安全呀。祝大家一路順風，旅途愉快。"},{"pid":"780926d0f49688f9f0ccf28b2f19d255f4ced183","tid":1404487,"uid":192994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:49:06.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n加借位<br />\n<br />\n[超合作運動] 會罷工既星期一都要返工<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dvxgxS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dvxgxS</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2fe3dfb5973fcef9472dd5fd77bdf85aca333836","tid":1404487,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:49:36.000Z","msg":"觀察到新戰術：四散游擊，街坊落場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1402338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1402338</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"16e8408d86e2fa8de7cf02d3a143899425ec4800","tid":1404487,"uid":248470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:50:09.000Z","msg":"非《一次又一次難清場》<br />\n是《一次又一次難拉人》"},{"pid":"1e5b591fcb008f504253686878eee20fabd0a812","tid":1404487,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"549a3e37ca2e4d4bb5418711d918bdd713764bff","tid":1404487,"uid":146499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:50: